      "title": "E235｜20年内CAR-T治愈癌症？与刘诚博士聊聊癌症治疗的底层哲学",
      "url": "https://aphid.fireside.fm/d/1437767933/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/90f96f60-25be-45ac-b832-56776a23d534.mp3",
